&lt;p&gt;The Project Manager will support projects across NYC’s commercial and industrial corridors, with a focus on priority sectors including technology, life sciences, advanced manufacturing, green economy, and other emerging industries. The role requires strong relationship-building and proactive lead generation, including engagement with brokers, property owners, site selectors, BIDs, chambers of commerce, local economic development organizations, community stakeholders, and international partners. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working closely with the Director of Business Development, this position will help strengthen NYC’s competitiveness, grow the business attraction pipeline, and create economic opportunities for New Yorkers.&lt;/p&gt;
