&lt;li&gt;Advise businesses and their management teams on relocation or expansion opportunities in NYC, including site selection, incentives, workforce connections, and strategic ecosystem introductions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist businesses in evaluating commercial and industrial real estate opportunities, including neighborhood fit, operational needs, workforce access, and ecosystem alignment.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
